message.body: Still up for having dinner tomorrow night or meeting for a drink? I just left D a voicemail asking what he's up to too. We could cook. Or go out.
Hey###### Just heard back from Daniel. Gonna meet him after he drops Junior at soccer tomorrow night - guessing around 6:30ish. You still up for hanging?
Yeah I could do a little hangout. Let me know the details.
Ok, not sure what we're gonna do. Maybe cook something? Maybe go out? Open to whatever.
Great, Let me know, I'll do whatever
Ok, sounds good. Not sure what D will feel like doing. I have a nice bottle of red that I wouldn't mind sharing. I'll text you tomorrow and we can make a plan.
